-bang7 Siong7-te3 pang-chan7¡¨. Kong2-liau2 chiu7 khi3. Hui7-bi2 ia7 eng7 ho2-oe7 an-ui3 so2-so2. Tui3 hit-am3 khi2 Hui7-bi2 koe3 lai5 kap A-so2 choe3 phoaN7, siong5-siong5 thak8 Seng3-keng saN an-ui3. 
  Kong2-kau3 Teng-liong5 kap peng5-iu2 hoe7 che5 liau2-au7 chiu7 tui3 Hun5-lam5 chhut-hoat tit8-tit8 ng3 lam5 kiaN5. Bian2 loa7 ku2 chiu7 kau3 kok-keng2 e5 pian-kai3. Keng-koe3 it-chhe3 e5 chhiu2-siok8 ho2-se3 chiu7 koe3 kok-keng2 jip8 Bian2-tian7 e5 pak-pou7 pian-kai3, koe3 Pa-ki-su-tan3 jip8 In3-tou7 e5 pak-peng5. Kau3 jip8 In3-tou7 e5 pak-peng5 e5 si5, lou7-chhau2 i3-goa7 e5 phaiN2, thiaN kong2 si7 ui7-tioh8 kin-ni5 e5 toa7 soat-pheng (Koan5 soaN e5 seh pang loh8--lai5) sou2 choe3 e5 toa7 chui2, kap kui2-na7 pai2 e5 te7-tang7 chhu7 soaN, ti3-kau3 eng2-koe3 u7 lou7 e5 sou2-chai7 soa3 piN3-choe3 bo5 lou7, ke chin hui-siong5 e5 phaiN2 kiaN5. Jit8-si5 kiaN5 am3-si5 hioh, siong5-siong5 koaN2 be7 kau3 sou2 ai3 kau3 e5 sou2-chai7, in chiu7 tah pou3-piN5 ti7 toa7 chhiu7 kha, a2-si7 kho3 toa7 chioh8-gam5 lai5 tah. Khiok ia7 che7, chio2 i2-keng u7 tui3 kui-hoa3 e5 hoan-a2 lai5 be2 tam7-poh8 siu3-phoe5.
  Kho2-sioh chit8-hang7 chiu7-si7 Teng-liong5 tauh-ti2 si7 thau5 chit8 hoe5, lou7 bo5-sek8, tak8-hang7 chheN-sou, ti7 peN5-lou7 chin gau5 phau2 be2, kau3 chia kam2-kak tak8-hang7 to bo5 li7-pian7, bo5 koan3-si3. Sou2-i2 tiaN7-tiaN7 kiaN5 choe3 au7-bin7. U7-si5 choe3 lok8-ngou2-chia2 toe3 be7 tioh8 tin7. Kai-chai3 Khun-hong-hiaN tai3-liam7 tioh8 tang5 bo2-hau7 chhut-sin e5 hau7-iu2, chiu7 siong5-siong5 tan2--i, u7 si5 tai7-ke hioh-khun3 khoaN3 bo5 Teng-liong5 e5 si5, i chiu7 koh hoe5-thau5 khi3 chhoe7. Chhin-chhiuN7 an2-ni m7-na7 chit8-pai2, Teng-liong5 ka-ti7 ia7 kam2-kak tui3 pat8 e5 tui7-oan5 chin put-chu7. Na7-si7 tai7-ke khiok long2 hian2-chhut tang5-kiaN5 chiu7-si7 tang5-mia7 e5 ho2-i3 bo5 lang5 koe3-chek--i, na7-si7 i ka-ti7 sim-lai7 chin lan5-koe3. U7 chit8-me5 ti7 tou5-tiong tu2-tioh8 toa7-hou7, hou7 chhin-chhiuN7 kheng-phun5 (kui-phun5 e5 chui2 teh piaN3 loh8-lai5) e5 se3-bin7. Ji5-chhiaN2 bo5 goeh8 bo5 chheN, lou7 iu7 kut8, chin-chiaN3 si7 chhun3-pou7 lan5 heng5. Sui-jian5 iau2-boe7 kau3 u5-teng7 e5 lou7-cham7, kou-put-chiong chiu7 koat-teng7 ti7 lou7-tiong chhoe7 sek-tong3 e5 sou2-chai7 lai5 hioh-khun3. Tai7-ke chham-siong5 chiu7 tah pou3-piN5 ti7 toa7 chioh8-gam5 e5 e7-bin7. Cha2 bat thiaN hit kak-si3 bat u7 chheN-hoan chhut-chhau2 sou2-i2 tai7-ke chin keng2-kak (keng2-chheN2 cheng-sin5) tiuN-ti5.
  Tan7-si7 hit mi5 si7 bo5 goeh8 bo5 chheN hong-kak bo5 beng5(tang-sai lam5-pak jin7 be7 chin). Sit8-chai7 si7 chit8 e5 chin bo5 peng5-an e5 me5-hng. Che7-che7 lang5 long2 cheng-sin5 cheng-sin5 m7-kaN2 khun3. Na7-si7 Teng-liong5 m7-bat tu2-tioh8 chit-khoan2 e5 khun3-khou2, kak-tit chap8-ji7-hun e5 ia3-sian7. Koh ui7-tioh8 ak-hou7 u7 lioh8-a2 leng2-tioh8 e5 khoan2, thau5-khak hin5-hin5 tang7-tang7, to2-loh8-khi3 put-ti put-kak soa3 khun3 loh8-bin5. Hut-jian5 khoaN3 tioh8 phok-phok-thiau3 chhin-chhiuN7 se3-chiah chiau2-a2 kho2-ai3 e5 sio2-moai7 ti7 hng7-hng7 chau2 oa2 lai5 chiap-i, kio3 A-ko e5 khoan2-sit. Chong2-si7 i e5 bak8-chiu e5 si7-soaN3 si7 tit8-tit8 khoaN3 koe3 sio2-moai7 e5 au7-bin7, khia7 ti7 toa7-mng5 piN teh tan2--i e5 ai3-chhe Soat-mui5. Ah! Soat-mui5 li2 e5 bi5-chhio3 chaiN2-iuN7 sui2 kau3 an2-ni, oan2-ju5 chit8-lui2 kek8 kho2-ai3, kek8 kiau-hong (kiau-sek8 koh siu2) bi2-le7 e5 mui5-kui3. Tu2-tu2 khui hiong3 hu-kun hong3-chhut i choe3-ho2 e5 phang-bi7, kap hou7 lang5 khoaN3 liau2 sim ui7-tioh8 i lai5 to5-chui3 e5 kiau-thai3. Teng-liong5 siam2-koe3 sio2-moai7, bo5 kap sio2-moai7 chheng2-an tit8-tit8 chau2 kau3 toa7 mng5-piN lai5 chiap i e5 ai3-kheng Soat-mui5, Soat-mui5 siang-chhiu2 chhun khui-khui lai5 chiap i e5 tiong7-hu. Teng-liong5 chau2-oa2 pho7 Soat-mui5 ti7 heng-cheng5, be7 ki3-tit ti7 au7-bin7 u7 sio2-moai7, ti7 thiaN-mng5 khau2 u7 pe7-bo2 teh khoaN3, chiu7 pho7 Soat-mui5 chhim-chhim e5 jiat8-bun2 (chhin-jiat8 e5 saN-chim). Tu2 kak-tit chap8-ji7-ban7-hun e5 chhin-bit8 an-ui3 e5 si5, hut-jian5 u7 chhin-chhiuN7 chheng-thiN lok8-lui5 siam2-tian7 phek-lek8 e5 siaN, toa7 hoah ¡§chheN-hoan chhut-chhau2, choan5-oan5 chian3-tou3 chun2-pi7¡¨.
  M7-chai si7 hoah khah-kin2, a2-si7 chheng3-siaN khah kin2, tui7-tiuN2 thau5 mng5 e5 chheng3 i2-keng tan5. Teng-liong5 tui3 tiN-bit8 e5 bin5-bang7 kiaN chheN2, sim phok8-phok8-chheng2, chit8-sim chin kiaN, chit8-chun7 e5 leng2-hong chhoe--lai5 kat-tit thong seng-khu e5 ke-bo2-phoe5 long2 gia5 khi2--lai5. Soa3 lau5 chit8-sin e5 leng2-koaN7. Kam2-kak thau5-khak phoe5 soa3 phong3 khi2--lai5, kha soa3 phu5-phu5 m7-chai tioh8 choe3 sim2-mih8. Na7-si7 chit8-sim iau2 teh to5-chui3 i e5 bin5-bang7, oan2-jian5 chhin-chhiuN7 chin, teh siuN7 i kho2-ai3 e5 Mui5 chhin-chhiuN7 mui5-kui3 e5 sui2 koh phang, hit e5 kiau-thai3 e5 kho2-ai3. Hit e5 khi3-bi7 na2-chun2 iau2 tiau5 ti7 i e5 phiN7, kam2-kak ai3-kheng chu-tun5 e5 ian-chi hek8-chia2 u7 bak ti7 i e5 bin7, jiok8-chhiN2 jiok8-chui3 poaN3 chheN2 poaN3 bo5-chheN2 e5 sun3-kan, tui7-tiuN2 toa7-siaN hoah tioh8 bih-loh8 u3, kheN-a2 tui3-bin7 hit-peng5 e5 chheng3-siaN kin2 lai5, chit-peng5 e5 chheng3 ia7 phah, ti7 am3-me5 bo5 khoaN3 lang5-bin7, chu7-jian5 chhiu7-bak8 chioh8-thau5 long2 bo5 khoaN3 kiN3. Chi2 u7 khoaN3 khong-tiong chheng3-chi2 e5 hoe2-kng, tui3 an2-ni lai5 chhai-chhek tui3-tek8 e5 hong-kak kap hng7 kin7. Teng-liong5 chiah tui3 be5-bang7 kiaN-chheN2, chheN-kong5 sa chit8 ki-chheng3 ng3 tui3-tek8 e5 hong-kak ia7 phah khi3. Chit8-si5 chheng3-chi2 hiu-hiu kio3 e5 siaN thoan5 ti7 kheN-a2 kap soaN-piah e5 tiong-kan, ia7 tui3 hit e5 chheng3-chi2 e5 hoe2-kng sio2-khoa2 u7 khoaN3-tioh8 but8-the2 e5 chun5-chai7. Hoan-a2 chit-pai2 si7 chin u7 ke3-oe7-tek e5 chhut-chhau2, bok8-tek8 si7 ai3 chhiuN2 be2, in-ui7 in u7 8 chiah chin sui2 e5 be2. Ti7 kheN-a2 hit-bin7 teh phah-chheng3 e5 hoan si7 hi-tiong seng-se3 (ke-iaN3 hoah-hiam3 chng-choe3 che7-che7 lang5) , chheng3 tan5 e5 si5 siong5-siong5 thiaN in chhut toa7-siaN kui tin7 hoah-hiu, hit e5 hiu-hiu kio3 e5 siaN in7 moa2 soaN-kheN, put-ti put-kak sit8-chai7 hou7 lang5 kam2-kak sit-taN2, ki5-tiong Teng-liong5 si7 siang7-kiaN. Sim-lai7 seN-khi2 hou7-hoe2 e5 sim. Hoan-a2 ki5-sit8 iau2 u7 chit8-tin7 kho3 in e5 te7-se3, lou7-chhau2 sek8, tui3 au7-bin7 eng7 pe5--e5, tiam7-tiam7 pau-ui5--lai5, chhiu2 giah8 hoan-a2 pio, io ha5 hoan-to, bi oa2 lai5 kau3 chin pek-sin in long2 m7 chai, kou3 ng3 kheN-a2 hit-peng5, ng3 thau5-cheng5 phah-chheng3. Chit8 e5 hoan-a2 sun7 Teng-liong5 phah-chheng3 e5 hoe2-kng tui3 au7-bin7 eng7 pio-a2 choh8 khi3, pat8-lang5 e7-hiau2 bih ti7 u3-nih bo5 hiah khoai3 khoaN3 tioh8. Teng-liong5 be7 hiau2, bih bo5 ho2-se3, khut bo5 loh8 khi3, poaN3 sin lou7-chhut ti7 goa7 bin7. Sou2-i2 pio-a2 tui3 au7-bin7 chhak8--lai5 tui3-tui3 tioh8 kha-chiah phiaN sim, aih8 chit8-e7 thiaN-kiN3 u7 lang5 to2-loh8-khi3 e5 siaN. Koh u7 chit8 e5 ou-iaN2 thiau3-oa2 lang5 to2-loh8-khi3 e5 sou2-chai7. Li7 Teng-liong5 iok 20 pou7 cho2-iu7 si7 Khun-hong bih ti7 chit8 te3 gam5-chioh8 e5 piN-ah, i te7-lak8-kam2 e5 tit8-kak si7 kong2 chham2-lah, chhut-su7 lah. Hoan-a2 pek-oa2, tong5-su7 sun2-sit lah. Sou2-i2 kin2-chiong i seng pi7-pan7 ti7 sin-piN e5 chhiu2-liu5-tan5 chhut-lat8 tim3 tui3 lang5 to2-loh8-khi3, kap ou-iaN2 thiau3 oa2-khi3 e5 sou2-chai7. Hut-jian5 pok8-chou3 e5 siaN chin kiong5-liat8, toe3 hit e5 pok8-cha3 ia7 hoat-chhut hoe2-kng, khoaN3-kiN3 toe3 siaN chit8 e5 ou-toa7-han3 chhiu2 giah8 chit8-ki peh8 ki3-ki3 e5 hoan-to, ai-chit8-siaN chin toa7 siaN chu7 an2-ni ia7 to2 loh8 khi3, tu2-tu2 siang3 tui3 tai7-seng to2 loh8-khi3 Teng-liong5 e5 sin-piN, chiau3-khoaN3 hit e5 hoan-a2 si7 beh lai5 cham7 Teng-liong5 e5 thau5-khak, soa3 poeh8 i e5 pio-a2 e5 khoan2, koh sun7 chhiu2-liu5-tan5 pok8-cha3 e5 hoe2-kng chiah khoaN3 tioh8 iau2-u7 kui2-na7-e5 hoan-a2 ku-ku teh chau2 ti7 au7-bin7, Khun-hong hoan-sin eng7 te2-chheng3 koh phah-si2 chit8 e5. Tui7-tiuN2 eng7 tng5-chheng3 ia7 phah si2 chit8 e5. Tui3 an2-ni hoan-a2 hoah the3-chui2, thiN i2-keng phah-phu2 kng lah, chit e5 hiam2-tiuN5 chiah koe3. 
  Sit8-chai7 si7 chit8-tiuN5 e5 khou2-chian3. ThiN kng kiam2-tiam2 jin5, be2, hoe3-mih8 chiah chai Teng-liong5 chha-put-to bo5 ng3-bang7 lah. In-ui7 hit ki hoan-a2-pio si7 tui3 khah-chiah-phiaN-sim tuh8 jip8 kau3 sim-chong7, ji5-chhiaN2 pio-a2-boe2 u7 boah tok8-ioh8. Hoeh lau5 chin-che7, bin7 long2 pian3-sek, gan2-sin5 ia7 long2 pian3 lah, kong2-oe7 long2 sit-siaN lah. Tai7-ke chin iu-bun7, m7-ku2 ia7 be7-tit ui7 i chit8 e5 choan5-tui7 lai5 ti7 chia tam-ian5 siuN ku2 (tam-gou7 ian5-oan7). Khun-hong chin chhin-chhiat phak loh8-khi3 thou5-nih lai5 thiaN i kong2-oe7. 
  SiaN toan7-toan7 siok8-siok8, bak8-sai2 si3-lam5-sui5. Hit e5 oe7 tai7-khai3 si7 kong2 an2-ni, ¡§Ah! tui3..... tui3 tai7-ke..... chin put..... put-chu7.....¡¨ theng5 chin ku2 long2 bo5 koh chhut-siaN, Khun-hong ka7 i an-ui3 io5-chhiu2 kong2 ¡§be7-be7.¡¨ Ia7 theh8 chhiu2-kin-a2 ka7 i chhit bak8-sai2. Kau3-boe2 bak8-chiu koh thi2-kim kong2 ¡§Chiong..... chiong goa2 e5 thau5..... thau5-mng5 koah chit8-chit8 sut-sut-a2..... theh8 to3 khi3 hou7..... ¡¨, soa3 hau2 chhut-lai5 chu7 an2-ni be7 koh kong2, Khun-hong ka7 i kong2 ¡§Li2 si7 kio3-goa2 koah li2 e5 thau5-mng5 theh8 to3-khi3 hou7 li2 e5 pe7-bo2 kap hu7-jin5-lang5 khoaN3 a2 m7-si7.¡¨ Hit-si5 i2-keng be7 hiau2 in3, kan-ta tim3-thau5. Chu7 an2-ni thau5-khak kau loh8-khi3 khui3-tng7. Khun-hong chiau3 i e5 i3-su3 chiu7 ka7 i koah tam7-poh8 thau5-mng5 khi2-lai5, koh tui3 saN ka7 i koah nng7-liap8 liu2-a2 si7 tang5-e5 sui2-sui2 ka7 i pau choe3-hoe2. Koh kiam2-tiam2 pat8-mih8, chiu7 chai chit8-chiah be2 sio2-khoa2 tioh8-siong ki5-u5 bo5 sit-loh8. Tui3 an2-ni m7-kaN2 koh chhian5-oan7, kin2-kin2 chiong Teng-liong5 e5 sin-si ka7 i khng3 ti7 chit8 e5 toa7-chioh8 khang, teng2-bin7 koh kng kui2-na7 te3 chioh8 ka7 i teh-leh, eng7 to ka7-i khek chit8 e5 sip8-ji7-ke3 e5 ki3-ho7, jian5-au7 chiu7 kin2 li7-khui hit sou2-chai7, in-ui7 kiaN-liau2 hoan-a2 khi3 tho2 kiu3-peng, beh po3 oan-siu5 chiu7 ka-poe7 e5 jin5-sou3 lai5 pau-ui5. Hit-si5 koaN2 put-tek8-chiong3 chiu7 toa7 li7-hai7, sou2-i2 me5-jit8 kiam-heng5 long2 m7-kaN2 koh theng5 kha. Hoan-a2 chin-chiaN3 m7-goan7 koh tui--lai5. 
